cmnh1sk7u0076k908pgy1fm8v	cmnh1sk3c003tk908gigp09oy	cmnh1sk7g006uk908osouksyu	activity	A4.1	Participatory design and agreement of governance structures, roles, and responsibilities for the commercialization network.	Facilitate participatory workshops and consensus-building sessions with cooperative leadership and MSME representatives to define governance bodies, decision-making rules, membership criteria, scheduling mechanisms, and cost-sharing arrangements for joint commercialization.	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	not_started	0	t	2026-04-02 05:42:21.019	2026-04-02 05:42:21.019
