cmnh1sk82007ck908weg2vivi	cmnh1sk3c003tk908gigp09oy	cmnh1sk7g006uk908osouksyu	activity	A4.4	Strategic Linkages and Export Readiness for the U.S. Market.	Pre-Establish formal contacts and hold technical meetings with key organizations to align project outputs with U.S. market requirements. This includes: Regulatory Compliance: Meetings with PROCOMER and the U.S. Agricultural Affairs Office (FAS) to identify FDA/FSMA requirements for the new value-added products. Business Networking: Outreach to the American Chamber of Commerce (AmCham) and U.S.-based business development organizations to explore partnership opportunities. Specialized Training: Integration of a specific module within the commercial training program (Outcome 1) focused exclusively on the U.S. Market. This chapter will cover market entry strategies, consumer trends, and practical steps to meet U.S. import standards, contributing to the required 80 person-hours in trade and investment.	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	not_started	3	t	2026-04-02 05:42:21.026	2026-04-02 05:42:21.026
cmnh1sk84007ek908mdbgvsuh	cmnh1sk3c003tk908gigp09oy	cmnh1sk7g006uk908osouksyu	activity	A4.5	Participatory design and pilot of a collaborative commercialization mechanism.	Using the improved production information and product consistency, support the cooperative and MSMEs to design and pilot a simple collaborative commercialization mechanism  for access to national buyers and potential future export channels.	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	not_started	4	t	2026-04-02 05:42:21.028	2026-04-02 05:42:21.028
cmnh2vd0g00b1k908kfjtns4s	cmnh2vczk00ack908qnv5kdsb	cmnh2vczz00ank908ryfmcnlb	objective	OE2	Capacitar a MiPYMEs en modelos de negocio sostenibles	Se busca capacitar a las MiPYMEs en la implementación de modelos de negocios sostenibles que les permitan desarrollar sus industrias comunitarias de manera rentable y respetuosa con el medio ambiente. Esto incluye la enseñanza de estrategias de gestión empresarial, eficiencia productiva agrícola, gestión de calidad y seguridad alimentaria industrial, e innovación comercial.	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	not_started	1	t	2026-04-02 06:12:31.264	2026-04-02 06:12:31.264
