cmnh1sk86007gk908gjeprgf2	cmnh1sk3c003tk908gigp09oy	\N	problem_statement	PS1	Problem statement	The agro-food MSMEs in the rural Los Santos region of San José, Costa Rica, face multiple challenges that limit their productivity, competitiveness, and ability to access higher-value national and export markets. These challenges include lack of business formalization, insufficient financial management, low export readiness, and limited digitalization of their production and commercial processes.\n\nAdditionally, these organizations operate with constrained financial and technical resources in a rural context, making it difficult to adopt conventional digital and automation solutions. The absence of a shared maquila/bio-refinery that adds value to coffee by-products and other local agricultural products restricts product diversification, quality consistency, and access to competitive markets.\n\nThe lack of process monitoring systems, light automation, and collaborative commercialization mechanisms limits these MSMEs’ capacity to reduce losses, comply with food safety regulations, and effectively coordinate market entry.\n\nTherefore, the target population requires accessible, low-cost, and sustainable solutions that strengthen their business and technical capacities, drive digital transformation, and foster collaborative approaches to production and commercialization. This project aims to address these needs through specialized training, digital tools, the establishment of a shared maquila/bio-refinery, monitoring systems, and a collaborative commercialization network, thereby promoting positive economic and social change for the MSMEs, their workers, and the local community.	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	not_started	0	t	2026-04-02 05:42:21.031	2026-04-02 05:42:21.031
cmnh1sk8a007ik9085h5zcvfb	cmnh1sk3c003tk908gigp09oy	\N	need	N1	Needs Outcome 1	Limited business formalization, weak financial management, low export readiness, lack of affordable digital tools.	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	not_started	1	t	2026-04-02 05:42:21.034	2026-04-02 05:42:21.034
cmnh1sk8c007kk908izuu3eg2	cmnh1sk3c003tk908gigp09oy	\N	need	N2	Needs Outcome 2	No shared maquila/bio-refinery, limited processing infrastructure, need for low-cost equipment.	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	\N	not_started	2	t	2026-04-02 05:42:21.037	2026-04-02 05:42:21.037
